    "body": "The idea behind defining these once is that it reduces the amount of allocations.\r\nYour idea of defining them as functions would defeat the purpose as it would create a new allocation on each call.\r\nYou're right that they could be changed by `Set` etc. However we make sure not to do that in the code ever and to only use them as arguments to functions that don't modify them",
